Name: Starlight  Emerald Lv.3
Description: Through Gemcrafting, raw ore can be processed into a higher-level Emerald.
Description$english: Through Gemcrafting, raw ore can be processed into a higher-level Emerald.
Description2$english: A rare raw stone grown in Regnus, displaying a green hue like a deep lake in the basin. A breeze sweeps through the valley, leaves dance lightly, standing like feathers on the green waves. Everything happens quietly, only the gem sleeping at the bottom of the lake witnesses this moment.
